OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777551071
OL,3,CHealth and education: The pressures
OL,4,Cfacing the next Welsh government
OL,6,FITV News Wales Reporter Rhys Williams
OL,7,Fhas travelled the length of the
OL,8,Fcountry to understand the impact the
OL,9,Ftwo main election issues, health and
OL,10,Feducation, are having on people's
OL,11,Flives, and what they want to change.
OL,13,FWales spends more per person on public
OL,14,Fservices than England. Yet in the two
OL,15,Fbiggest areas controlled by the Welsh
OL,16,Fgovernment, education and health,
OL,17,Foutcomes are often worse.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777551071
OL,3,CHealth and education: The pressures
OL,4,Cfacing the next Welsh government
OL,6,FWales has lagged behind the rest of
OL,7,Fthe UK on reading, maths and science
OL,8,Ffor two decades, while patients are
OL,9,Fmuch more likely to be stuck on long
OL,10,Fhospital waiting lists.
OL,12,FWhat, then, is going wrong? Ahead of a
OL,13,Fvital Senedd election next week, it's
OL,14,Fa question many voters will be asking
OL,15,Fand something the next Welsh
OL,16,Fgovernment will need to answer.
OL,18,FIn a classroom in Cardiff, a group of
OL,19,FYear 7 pupils are trying to get on the
OL,20,Fsame page.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
