OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777551071
OL,3,CHealth and education: The pressures
OL,4,Cfacing the next Welsh government
OL,6,FLike in comprehensive schools across
OL,7,FWales, many have arrived at Willows
OL,8,FHigh School having learned very
OL,9,Fdifferent things.
OL,11,FThat's because, in Wales, there is no
OL,12,Flonger a set list of topics that every
OL,13,Fchild must learn, so what pupils are
OL,14,Ftaught can vary widely from one
OL,15,Fprimary school to another.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
