OL,3,CHealth and education: The pressures
OL,4,Cfacing the next Welsh government
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FCritics say it's a similar story in
OL,12,Fthe NHS. Like in schools, spending per
OL,13,Fperson on health in Wales is higher
OL,14,Fthan in England, with a significant
OL,15,Fincrease in staffing in recent years.
OL,16,FBut the number of treatments has not
OL,17,Fkept pace and outcomes are often worse.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777551071
OL,3,CHealth and education: The pressures
OL,4,Cfacing the next Welsh government
OL,6,FIn England, waits of more than two
OL,7,Fyears for treatment have effectively
OL,8,Fbeen eliminated. In Wales, although
OL,9,Ftimes are falling, thousands of
OL,10,Fpatients are still waiting that long.
OL,12,FIn rural mid-Wales, Susan Williams
OL,13,Ftells me she's been waiting more than
OL,14,Ftwo years for surgery on her spine and
OL,15,Fstill doesn't know when the operation
OL,16,Fwill take place. Sue is a school bus
OL,17,Fdriver and worries that she'll soon
OL,18,Fhave to give up a job she loves as the
OL,19,Fpain intensifies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777551071
OL,3,CHealth and education: The pressures
OL,4,Cfacing the next Welsh government
OL,6,F"They told me I'd been waiting 69
OL,7,Fweeks - then said the wait was now 140
OL,8,Fweeks. I just don't understand how
OL,9,Fthat happens."
OL,11,F"It does get you down. You do feel
OL,12,Fquite depressed at times, because
OL,13,Fyou're in pain all the time and you
OL,14,Fdon't know when it's going to end."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777551071
OL,3,CHealth and education: The pressures
OL,4,Cfacing the next Welsh government
OL,6,FBut the reasons behind those longer
OL,7,Fwaits are complex. Many point to Wales
OL,8,Fhaving an older, poorer and therefore
OL,9,Fsicker population. But the IFS says
OL,10,Fthat despite increased funding and
OL,11,Fstaffing, the number of patients being
OL,12,Ftreated has not risen at the same
OL,13,Frate, which suggests a problem with
OL,14,Fproductivity.
OL,16,FRecovery from the pandemic has also
OL,17,Fbeen slower than in England, and
OL,18,Fdifferences in how services are
OL,19,Forganised may also play a role.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777551071
OL,3,CHealth and education: The pressures
OL,4,Cfacing the next Welsh government
OL,6,FIn the waiting room at Clerk Avenue
OL,7,FSurgery in Cwmbran, a teary-eyed Sarah
OL,8,Ftells me she waited two and a half
OL,9,Fyears waiting to be treated for an
OL,10,Fembarrassing bladder problem.
OL,12,F"It was really frustrating, because
OL,13,Fyou just feel like you're not being
OL,14,Flistened to."
OL,16,FShe also suffered with mental health
OL,17,Fproblems due to the wait.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777551071
OL,3,CHealth and education: The pressures
OL,4,Cfacing the next Welsh government
OL,6,FGP Dr Gareth Oelmann says demand is
OL,7,Frising faster than the system can cope
OL,8,Fwith, and that more money is needed to
OL,9,Ffund GPs.
OL,11,F"We know that 90% of contacts within
OL,12,Fthe NHS are on General Practice level,
OL,13,Ffor just 6% of the budget."
OL,15,F"We need to focus more upon prevention
OL,16,Frather than just fighting the fires."
OL,18,FWhoever forms the next Welsh
OL,19,Fgovernment, these are the significant
OL,20,Fpressures they will inherit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30218
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777551071
OL,3,CHealth and education: The pressures
OL,4,Cfacing the next Welsh government
OL,6,FWith an election just a week away, all
OL,7,Fthe main parties say they want to
OL,8,Fimprove public services. Many are
OL,9,Fpromising more investment and more
OL,10,Fstaff.
OL,12,FBut money alone may not be enough. The
OL,13,Fbigger challenge will be to close the
OL,14,Fgap between what is spent, and what
OL,15,Fpeople experience.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
